Built for Ubuntu, could work in other flavors of Debian. Install a fully functional version right from de repo of github. 
Any comments or workarounds will greatfully revised. 
Software to make lectures of petri dishes, colony count. 
Github https://github.com/qgeissmann/OpenCFU.git 
OpenCFU was created by Quentin Geissmann, with improvements by Nathananael Lampe and Mac Cowell.
